description:
Does Adam Savage have a favorite found-object artist? Why is the cleanliness of the prison on Narkana 5 so terrifying in Andor? In this live stream excerpt, Adam answers these questions from Tested members Erlasdottir and Seth Huckstead, whom we thank for their support!
